= with_named_scope

  This is a monkey patch for using the patch I submitted here:
  http://rails.lighthouseapp.com/projects/8994-ruby-on-rails/tickets/739

== Description

== Installation

=== Archive Installation

	rake install

=== Gem Installation

	gem install with_named_scope

== Features/Problems

  * Scoped block for named_scope
  * Introduces AR.identity scope

== Synopsis

  User.active.with_scope do
    User.count #=> equals to User.active.count
  end

  User.identity.count #=> User.count

